name: Relax & Trust God
description:
Enrich your wardrobe with a versatile long sleeve Faith Tee. For a casual look, combine it with your favorite jeans, and layer it with a button-up shirt, a zip-up hoodie, or a cute jacket.

 

• 100% combed and ring-spun cotton
• Heather colors are 52% combed and ring-spun cotton, 48% polyester
• Athletic Heather is 90% combed and ring-spun cotton, 10% polyester
• 32 singles
• Retail fit
• Crew neck
• Cover-stitched collar
• 2'' ribbed cuffs
• Side-seamed
additionalInfoDescription1: Orders usually ship within 10-15 days. There may be possible delays due to Covid 19.

name: For His Glory Half Zip Sweatshirt
description:
This is our trendy half zip sweatshirt designed with our logo on front and a inspirational message for you to display to the world on back. Layer this one up or wear it on its own for a contemporary look.

 

  • Double needle shoulder, cuffs and waistband
  • 1X1 rib on cuffs and waistband
  • Sideseamed
  • Twill label
  • Twill taped back neck
  • Self fabric lined collar
  • Soft washed garment dyed fabric
